reviewText: Tony Little's workout is great. The half an hour goes by quickly and you are getting a good workout in the comfort of your own home.

i love this workout,because i already had the gazelle machine, so i ordered the tape to be able to guide me thru a full body workout, and it was truly amazing. i lost weight like crazy. it's diffidently a advanced workout.
Tony Little talks too much in this video. It really stinks. He just doesn't shut up! It was a cheap waste of money.
